disc_desc:
Additional comments on cultural manifestations;
Tracks of side RR track are still in the pavement of Belmont St.  Well is still intact.  1/2 of an original wooden plank was saved.

Depot burned in early 1940's the lot has been vacant since then.  It will become a new depot replica in Nov. 2002.  The Allen Station (1874) Dam Artifacts will also be displayed in the new replica of the train depot.  City marker only.

